---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SocialLinks from "../components/SocialLinks.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Omar Maaouane Veiga" description="A bit about Omar Maaouane Veiga — data-driven engineer based in London.">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      Hello! My name is Omar Maaouane Veiga, I am a London-based engineer with a background in robotics
      and programming. I love making useful systems that people can use. Whether it's to get a
      chuckle from them or for legitimate use, that's what tech is needed for right? To make our lives better
      in some way.
    </p>

    <!-- ── Hero gallery ── -->
    <div class="gallery">
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/media/sigma-labs/Sigma_Patagonia.jpg" alt="Omar in Patagonia" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/media/RIAT/RIAT_Typhoon.jpg" alt="Omar posing in front of Spanish Typhoon at RIAT airshow" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/media/uni-life/uni_pic.jpg" alt="University days" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/media/worldskills/WS_Bro_Pic.jpg" alt="Omar WS picture with his teammate" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/media/worldskills/WS_Mandem.jpg" alt="WS picture with my teammate and other friends we met" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/media/worldskills/WS_Pic_System.jpg" alt="WS systems pic" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/media/worldskills/WS_Pic.jpg" alt="Omar at work" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <h2>What I work with</h2>

      <p>
        I could list off technologies and projects all day but it'd be faster to just say that
        I'm a computer nerd with a big taste in practical electronics. Yes I code, but I also solder
        things together into inventions that make use of that code.
      </p>

      <p>
        Python is my go-to for wrangling data. If something needs a backend, an API,
        or just a script that saves someone three hours a week, I'll build it. And if
        the problem lives in the physical world — sensors, motors, embedded boards —
        even better I'll usually switch over to C++.
      </p>

      <h2>How I work</h2>

      <p>
        Honestly? I just talk to people. The most important part of any project is knowing what you or
        the client has to do. Once I have solid list of requirements, I'll plan out a timeline and get to work!
        I move fast, keep things simple, and try not to build anything that needs a manual
        to understand. An intuitive product is a product that makes all of this fancy tech
        actually useful to anybody other than me.
      </p>

      <h2>Beyond work</h2>

      <p>
        When I'm not neck-deep in code or circuits, I'm probably tinkering with some
        side project that caught my eye, folding origami, modelling characters in
        Blender, or even geeking out over fighter jets at an airshow.
        I like building things, breaking things, and figuring out how things work.
        That's me in a nutshell.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>

      <p>
        If any of this sounds like your kind of conversation, I'm always up for a
        chat. Drop me an email or find me on LinkedIn — I don't bite.
      </p>

      <SocialLinks variant="labeled" size={20} />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* ── Photo gallery (CSS columns masonry) ── */
  .gallery {
    columns: 3;
    column-gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .gallery-item {
    break-inside: avoid;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .gallery-item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, filter 0.4s ease;
    filter: grayscale(20%);
  }

  .gallery-item:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.03);
    filter: grayscale(0%);
  }

  /* ── About content ── */
  .about-content {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-content ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .gallery {
      columns: 2;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .gallery {
      columns: 1;
    }
  }
</style>
